      "label": "Condition",
      "value": "The papyrus has been glued onto cardboard which makes it impossible to read the verso side. On the right side at least two words are missing in every line. On the left side the original cutting line is partially visible. At the top the papyrus has been broken off above the text. The right corner at the top and bottom have been broken off. From the left side four pieces have been torn off. The papyrus fibres have been crumpled or have some loose in several places."
    },
